    "These models www.nature.com/scientificreports/ for classifying drivers of forest loss were implemented and run in the Sepal geospatial analysis platform (SEPAL 2.0) 37, a cloud-based computing environment offered by FAO, with instance type g8, which provides NVIDIA Tesla M60 GPUs with 32GB of VRAM.",
